{"type": "article", "id": 7500, "title": "Kwik-E-Mart 辛普森一家积木", "description": "", "date": "2015-03-18T07:22:42Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 8, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605234205OsBZeSVR5P2vkJE6.png", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t继去年的 Simpson House LEGO 积木套装爆红之后，LEGO 今年又推出了“辛普森一家” Kwik-E-Mart 新型积木套装。这个套装以 Kwik-E-Mart 超市为主题，包含 2179 块积木和 16 款不同的人偶积木。目前定价为 200 美元，将在 2015 年 5 月 1 日正式在<a href=\"http://shop.lego.com/en-US/\" target=\"_blank\">LEGO 线上</a>与线下商店同时与大家见面。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234202yRdiqjPO9JTgplvQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234203VBehdcLub9HQpkKw.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.55042017\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052342042mxJhLD3iq1pFTkz.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.5626327\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234204x1JmMBkSPN4HQV9s.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"1.11016949\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}